wnload report Consumer goods and retail outlook 2024A slowdown in inflation will bolster retail volume growth by 6.7% in US dollar terms and 2% in volume terms in 2024. However, reduced savings and high food prices, worsened by the effects of climate change, will act as dampeners. Download report Healthcare outlook 2024A recovery in the global economy will cause a return to spending growth in the healthcare sector. However, it will remain vulnerable to headwinds, including limited resources, stricter regulations and continued strikes. Download report Download the free report Fill in the form below:  *First name:*Last name:*Company:*Business email:*Job Title:*Business phone:*Industry:Select...Academia & EducationAdvertising, Marketing & PRAgriculture, Forestry & FishingAutomotiveAviation, Aerospace & DefenceCharities, Foundations & NGO'sChemicalsConstruction, Engineering & InfrastructureConsulting / Professional ServicesEnergy, Utilities & RenewablesFinancial servicesFMCGGovernment & Public ServicesHealthcare & PharmaceuticalsIndustrial goods & ManufacturingIT & TechnologyMedia & EntertainmentMetals & MiningReal EstateRetail & Consumer GoodsTelecommunicationsTransport, Logistics & Supply ChainTravel, Sports, Leisure, Tourism & HospitalityOther*Job function:Select...Advocacy / PolicyConsultingCorporate Development / Mergers & AcquisitionsData, Analytics and AIDesign, Pictures and Media ProductionEconomicsEducationEngineeringFinance / TreasuryGeneral ManagementGovernment and Public ServiceHR / PeopleInvestment ManagementIT / TechnologyJournalism, Reporting and EditorialLegal and ComplianceLibrarian / Information ManagementMarketing, Media, Brand, ProductOperations / Supply chainPoliticsProcurementProgram/Project ManagerPublic Relations and CommunicationsResearch / Business IntelligenceResearch & Development (R&D)RetiredRisk ManagementSales / Business developmentStrategy / PlanningStudent/Not currently employedSustainability / ESG / CSROther*Job level:Select...Analyst /